com.opcoach.training.rental
Interface Rental

All Known Implementing Classes:
RentalImpl
public interface Rental

A representation of the model object 'Rental'.

The following features are supported:

  • Customer
  • Rented Object
  • Start Date
  • End Date
  • Parent Agency
